        "title": "FIFA WC: Defending champion Argentina to take on Egypt; Switzerland vs Colombia",
        "summary": "In FIFA World Cup, defending champions Argentina will take on Egypt in Round of 16 match in Atlanta tonight. Later in another Round of 16 clash, Switzerland will face Colombia in Vancouver. Belgium defeated United States 4-1 in the Round of 16 clash in Seattle to secure their place in the quarterfinals of the tounament. […]",
        "article": "In FIFA World Cup, defending champions Argentina will take on Egypt in Round of 16 match in Atlanta tonight. Later in another Round of 16 clash, Switzerland will face Colombia in Vancouver. Belgium defeated United States 4-1 in the Round of 16 clash in Seattle to secure their place in the quarterfinals of the tounament. Belgium will now face Spain in the quarterfinals at the Los Angeles Stadium on Friday. Spain stormed into the quarter-finals beating Portugal 1-nil in the Round of 16 clash at the Dallas Stadium last night. England, Norway, Morocco and France have already entered quarter-finals.",
